      <div class="tech-card"><div class="tech-icon" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:28px;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:16px;">01</div><div class="tech-name">CEREC CAD/CAM</div><div class="tech-desc">Design, mill, and fit crowns, bridges, and veneers in one appointment. Bengaluru's only single-visit dentistry technology. Eliminates the need for temporary restorations or lab wait times.</div><div class="tech-badge">Single Visit Crowns</div></div>
      <div class="tech-card"><div class="tech-icon" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:28px;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:16px;">02</div><div class="tech-name">Waterlase iPlus Laser</div><div class="tech-desc">Water-activated laser for cavity preparation and root canals without traditional drills. Significantly less discomfort, faster healing, and often no anaesthesia required.</div><div class="tech-badge">Painless Root Canals</div></div>
      <div class="tech-card"><div class="tech-icon" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:28px;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:16px;">03</div><div class="tech-name">Biolase Soft Tissue Laser</div><div class="tech-desc">Precision gum reshaping and periodontal therapy. Minimal bleeding, no sutures needed, faster recovery. Used in gum contouring, lesion removal, and smile corrections.</div><div class="tech-badge">Laser Gum Treatment</div></div>
