      <div class="tech-card"><div class="tech-icon" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:28px;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:16px;">06</div><div class="tech-name">Dental Loupes</div><div class="tech-desc">High-magnification precision loupes used during every procedure. Allows detection of issues invisible to the naked eye — ensuring conservative treatments and better outcomes.</div><div class="tech-badge">Precision Dentistry</div></div>
