        <a href="#indiranagar" style="background:var(--offwhite);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 18px;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">Indiranagar Clinic FAQs <span style="color:var(--teal)">→</span></a>
